  <acronym>ALL2008con</acronym>
  <official_title>Nordic Society of Paediatric Haematology and Oncology Treatment Protocol for Children (1.0 - 17.9 Years of Age) and Young Adults (18-45 Years of Age) With ALL. Efficacy of Individualised 6MP Dosing During Consolidation Therapy</official_title>
